leve.name: Nothing Compares to Shrews
leve.description: It may surprise you, but the leading cause of injury to our organization's chocobos is not ambushes by bloodthirsty beastkin, but shrewhills! Stepping in one of these holes can snap a bird's leg in two, leaving him incapacitated for months...or in serious cases, force us to put him down. To see that our birds stay healthy, the Seventy-Seven Caravans will pay good coin for the head of every shrew delivered to our headquarters.
